                <mxCell id="n7" value="Lines 196-221: For each part in parts[], renders a &lt;PartLineCard&gt;&#10;→ src/components/common/PartLineCard.tsx : lines 40-152&#10;&#10;Each PartLineCard contains:&#10;  Part Number: SearchablePartPicker (combobox, must select from items, no free text)&#10;    → src/components/common/SearchablePartPicker.tsx : lines 15-29&#10;    Extra action: &quot;New Part&quot; button (line 211) → opens AddItemModal&#10;      → src/components/modals/AddItemModal.tsx — creates item inline via POST /api/items&#10;  Location: SearchableLocationPicker (combobox, must select from locations, no free text)&#10;    → src/components/common/SearchableLocationPicker.tsx : lines 15-29&#10;    Extra action: &quot;New Location&quot; button (line 216) → opens AddLocationModal&#10;      → src/components/modals/AddLocationModal.tsx — creates location inline via POST /api/locations&#10;    NOTE: Location is NOT auto-populated (unlike Sale form) — user must select manually&#10;  Quantity: &lt;Input type=&quot;number&quot; min=&quot;1&quot;&gt; — required, integer ≥ 1&#10;  Unit Cost: &lt;Input type=&quot;number&quot; step=&quot;0.01&quot; min=&quot;0&quot;&gt; — required, number ≥ 0&#10;  Currency: &lt;Select&gt; with hardcoded options: £, $, € (defaults to £)&#10;📄 src/components/receipts/AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 196-221" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="270" y="989" width="480" height="270" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

